headline: Think It's Too Late to Buy AMD? Here's the Biggest Reason Why There's Still Time.
summary: AMD often gets overlooked because of its distant second place in market share to Nvidia.  Several of AMD’s core markets are massive growth opportunities.  Advanced Micro Devices (NASDAQ: AMD), better known simply as AMD, is often overlooked by investors, as it has a distant second-place market share to leading chipmaker Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) in the AI-fueled data center accelerator market.
